                                        <h3> <img src="/assets/fleetnext_home_50.jpg">&nbsp;&nbsp;Oraganize all fleet data</h3>
                                        <p>Fleet administration is a tedious and time-consuming process. Information may be scattered across multiple spreadsheets, files, log books placed in different cabinets in multiple offices. Fleetnext helps you save time by storing vehicle data, tyre positions, service logs and much more in one secure place for quick online access 24 * 7 from any office or any branch. Any paperwork related to vehicles can be scanned & put into Fleetnext.</p>

                                        <h3> <img src="/assets/fleetnext_home_78.jpg">&nbsp;&nbsp;Scale on business growth</h3>
                                        <p>Fleetnext provides you with a robust, scalable fleet management platform that seamlessly accommodates additional workload and users as the size of your fleet grows.</p>

                                </div>
